name: Kim Lopez
summary: Kim Lopez is a 31-year-old Financial Analyst living in Los Angeles. She is originally from Houston, Texas and is a graduate of UC Berkeley. Kim identifies as a straight woman and lists her pronouns as she/her/hers. She values family, work-life balance, and empathy. Kim is an active advocate of a healthy lifestyle. Besides her work, she likes to spend her time hiking, reading, travelling, and cooking. Kim is a moderate and identifies as agnostic. She does not have children, but she is open to having some in the future. She specifies that she does not smoke or use drugs and only occasionally drinks. Kim is an ISFJ and a Libra. She is looking for a life partner aged between 30-40, who shares similar interests and values, does not smoke or use drugs but is okay with drinking sometimes.
